---
// Confirmation page after Matt submits the /matt form. Noindex.
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
<title>Thanks Matt — WCCP</title>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f7f5f0; color: #131E44; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 24px; line-height: 1.55; }
  .card { background: white; border-radius: 14px; max-width: 600px; width: 100%; padding: 36px 32px; box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(19,30,68,0.08); }
  .tick { width: 64px; height: 64px; background: #27ae60; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 20px; }
  .tick svg { width: 36px; height: 36px; fill: white; }
  h1 { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  h1 span { color: #f5c13b; }
  .lead { font-size: 16px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .panel { background: #f7f5f0; border-radius: 10px; padding: 18px 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .panel h2 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; color: #131E44; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .panel ul { list-style: none; }
  .panel li { font-size: 14px; padding: 6px 0; padding-left: 26px; position: relative; }
  .panel li::before { content: "✓"; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 6px; color: #27ae60; font-weight: 800; }
  .next { background: #f0f4ff; border-left: 4px solid #3a5cb5; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; padding: 14px 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .next h2 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; color: #1e3a8a; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .next p { font-size: 14px; color: #1e3a8a; }
  .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
  .footer a { color: #3a5cb5; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
  <div class="tick">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17 4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/></svg>
  </div>
  <h1>Got it, Matt — <span>thank you</span></h1>
  <p class="lead">Your answers have landed safely with the WCCP team.</p>

  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Where your answers are now</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Emailed straight to <strong>info@wccp.co.uk</strong></li>
      <li>Stored in our backup dashboard at Netlify</li>
      <li>Any files you uploaded are in the same place</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="next">
    <h2>What happens next</h2>
    <p>We'll go through your answers, update the website, and come back to you within 2 working days with anything that needs clarifying. If you remembered something else, you can fill the form again or just reply to the confirmation email.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    Need to add something? <a href="/matt">Open the form again</a><br>
    Urgent? Call us: <a href="tel:01409281437">01409 281437</a>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
